  {
    "row": 56,
    "rowsha": "j1UTu6udd9Braucj/hr2mXZi6e0yhcktkyk3fRd21Dk=",
    "originContent": "> Alternatively, you can also set `isDirect` to true thru the URL query by adding `?isDirect=true` at the end of your URL",
    "translatedContent": "> または、URLのクエリパラメータで `?isDirect=true` を追加して `isDirect` をtrueに設定することもできます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 57,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "4YWD/+z2ihXFN7QZ5v3N83uOx2BdRzxVgeNn6TMT7Gs=",
    "originContent": "### \"I don't see the video's caption!\"",
    "translatedContent": "### 「動画のキャプションが見えません！」"
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "BY2sPWie9p+fieQQdjeNg5L3gLSxRgItaB49HTh0P9U=",
    "originContent": "By default, we put the description into the `og:description` tag, but Discord removes that from the embed if there's a video inside the embed. We decided not to add it to the top like what [tfxktok.com](https://tfxktok.com) does to prevent the embed from getting too cluttered with hashtags.",
    "translatedContent": "デフォルトでは、説明文を `og:description` タグに入れていますが、Discordは埋め込み内に動画がある場合、そのタグを埋め込みから削除します。[tfxktok.com](https://tfxktok.com)がやっているように、ハッシュタグで埋め込みが煩雑になるのを防ぐために上部に追加しないことにしました。"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "eRETuJNrN18+B3JcSnvcbZrxOuyQl3Mpxbh2AzcLriY=",
    "originContent": "However, we want to give users the option to add it in case it brings additional context to the video. You can change your URL to `a.tnktok.com` to add the description to the top.",
    "translatedContent": "しかし、動画に追加の文脈を与える場合があるため、ユーザーが説明文を追加するオプションを提供したいと思います。URLを `a.tnktok.com` に変更すると説明文を上部に追加できます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "Yq2wPPnCXy301hjHCKFQIxODY4Rioi4Pr3L3gt9kyfM=",
    "originContent": "|         Before         |        After         |",
    "translatedContent": "|         変更前         |        変更後         |"
  },
  {
